data.description: This spacious home is located in the wonderful township of Cajah's Mountain NC. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for you and your loved ones. Situated on 1.63 acres, this property offers plenty of outdoor space for gardening, entertaining, AND MUCH MORE. The wood flooring throughout with beautiful fireplace adds a touch of warmth and elegance to the interior, also has a gorgeous view of table rock. One of the features of this property is the large detached garage and workshop. Whether you're a hobbyist in need of extra storage, this space offers endless possibilities. With its SOME recent updates and spacious layout, this house is ready for you to move in and make it your own. New dishwasher, hot water heater, new windows, mini spilt, carpet, green house and much more. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience all that this property has to offer! Buyers agent bonus is offered till 09/30/23
